{"tid":1481351,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"重症肌無力患者，請聯絡我","createTime":"2019-08-17T16:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:34:16.000Z","uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e382bfecd3ac2bd57593c4a4eecba01dc4898e","tid":1481351,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"聯絡方法<br />\nFb messager <a href=\"https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fseek.chinesemedicine.1&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1Ftn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=7787c01a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1</a><br />\nTg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Usernamennn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUsernamennn&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1Ftn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=902353d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Usernamennn</a><br />\n<br />\n男 24歲<br />\n12年9月開始疲倦至今<br />\n14年5月開始嚴重地病，停學3年<br />\n<br />\n症狀：<br />\n四肢乏力,手：愈近末梢，愈少力。之前最嚴重時，切兩個橙，手好快疲倦，要休息<br />\n職業治療檢查:合上眼後手指頭不太能分辨尖、頓<br />\n手小肌肉做重複性動作後很容易累。<br />\n腳：行約1小時覺累，要休息。腳板比病發前闊，要買加加寬版鞋穿。<br />\n全身：試過拿3.5公斤走10分鐘，非常累。<br />\n無骨傷史。無地貧。<br />\n<br />\n睡眠正常。背易出汗，手腳掌經常出汗。<br />\n胃口較大。每天喝水約1.5公升。水喝常溫無偏好。<br />\n不會特別怕冷或熱。小便開叉。陰莖勃起後好像易軟。大便正常，但喝中藥後大便溏腳板脫皮。吃寒涼食物後偶會不精神。<br />\n吃辣的食物偶會臉和頸的皮膚痛。頸和手臂有細細粒。<br />\n<br />\n5-8年前，曾經常太多龜苓膏、涼茶造成經常腹瀉，之後愈來愈累<br />\n<br />\n西醫:看過腦神經內科,等內科神經傳導檢查中。<br />\n照過胸背x光。<br />\n有脂肪肝。<br />\n14年驗出肝酵素高。<br />\n17年照胃鏡，有胃炎。<br />\n<br />\n中藥處方<br />\n<a href=\"https://photos.app.goo.gl/9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotos.app.goo.gl%2F9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1Ftn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=604a163d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://photos.app.goo.gl/9MZZuLHDzs1esvbA6</a><br />\n<br />\n病情討論fb gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/954306168239427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F954306168239427&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1Ftn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=584e968c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/954306168239427</a><br />\n病情討論tg gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1Ftn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=983f1adb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyBRjAYZAparanxCZUA</a>"},{"pid":"8e8045be29e67685a13f5f9c2314bb6824fd38db","tid":1481351,"uid":294133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"係咪無得醫"},{"pid":"6a3ef4b9e4fb2aae59496fb43ba44d8b31da41fa","tid":1481351,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e8045be29e67685a13f5f9c2314bb6824fd38db","tid":1481351,"uid":294133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"係咪無得醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"有"}]}